.el .ds Aq '
.TH antimony-edit 1  "edit " 
.SH NAME
antimony\-edit \- Edit an existing profile
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBantimony edit\fR [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-feature\fR] [\fB\-s\fR|\fB\-\-system\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fINAME\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Edit an existing profile
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-feature\fR
Target the feature set rather than the profile set
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-system\fR
Target the system set rather than the user set
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fINAME\fR>
The object to edit
